        <Parent_String>lacing needles [300022936], leatherworking needles [300022932], leatherworking tools [300395476], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
